OL,3,CConcerns over fairness of new Guernsey
OL,4,CPolice complaints process
OL,6,FA former Guernsey Chief Minister is
OL,7,Fraising concerns about a new police
OL,8,Fcomplaints process in the island, and
OL,9,Fis calling for it to be annulled.
OL,11,FDeputy Gavin St Pier says a new
OL,12,Fcomplaints system is unfair and leaves
OL,13,Fcomplainants without the opportunity
OL,14,Fto appeal a decision that is made.
OL,16,FThe process allows police to analyse
OL,17,Fevidence, including bodycam footage,
OL,18,Fand consider if there is merit to a
OL,19,Fcomplaint.
