OL,3,CConcerns over fairness of new Guernsey
OL,4,CPolice complaints process
OL,6,FUnder the previous process, Guernsey
OL,7,FPolice would investigate a complaint
OL,8,Fif gross misconduct or misconduct was
OL,9,Flikely to be the proven outcome.
OL,11,FDeputy Gavin St Pier is calling for
OL,12,Fthe new process to be annulled so that
OL,13,Fthe island's politicians can consider
OL,14,Fwhether they think it is right for
OL,15,Fislanders.
